                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.113 Airplanes/9: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-06-23T12:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 23, 1928—noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>198. Your 484, June 20, 8 p.m. The Department will grant permits to export
                    commercial airplanes to China.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
